## Quick Start

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/CausalEcho.git
cd CausalEcho
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Scan a file
python causal_echo_detector.py "videos/ceo_resignation.mp4"

# Scan a folder
python causal_echo_detector.py "./tiktok_downloads/" --threshold 0.8

# Live webcam truth mirror
python webcam_realtime.py
